Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就让那个孩子觉醒为神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧时间准备仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前你母亲和你的力量曾救过我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算拼上性命也要救出你的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想离开这里 去见那个叫姆伽罗的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去见姆伽罗妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事想见面确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德·达克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫平恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之护佑与我同在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边就交给你们几个了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 还不能剧烈活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个恶魔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我跟狄亚思解决掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪我没救下她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我始终不认为那人配当奥尔良骑士团的团长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一只受伤的恶魔手上拯救人民都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种人当团长我无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么灰心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也是上面决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们根本改变不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计上面人喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是美女团长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 团长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没把握好轻重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来换我当你对手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前 我杀害了神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了圣女应有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此深重的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便献上我的生命也偿还不清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 我依然想以骑士的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的罪行没能挽救的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无力的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要背负这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃避很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我还不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被解除团长一职前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望尽全力当好奥尔良骑士团的团长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会追随你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神都不在就要继位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样行得通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是新的亚纳提王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利欧斯17世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类畏惧恶魔 崇拜神明的时代必将结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此向大家保证
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会创造出人类盛世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下还望三思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何要进攻众神殿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对创造人类盛世有帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很确定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人与神长久以来的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要以这种方式断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些东西必须要弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可神却拒绝交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此就只能抢过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下所指的东西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯听命于我 就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个国家里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今仍有跟你一样崇拜神明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 只要原圣女肯听命于我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必那帮人也会放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选吧 贞德·达克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是听命于我 共创人类盛世呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是离开王都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 后面就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选吧 贞德·达克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 屋子不会被吹跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个...不好说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫贞德·达克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我儿子 艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德·达克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说她偷偷住在郊外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可实在没想到她有孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 竟然拥有能令漆黑兵无力化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不是跟人类生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子要是到神手上就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经封堵了她的逃跑路线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将她逼向王都了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住她应该只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论生死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要別让她把孩子交给神就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没收获
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定把她逼到这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的命令 找到就立刻杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分三路行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要杀我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去那边找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 看那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去里面找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现就立即杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要活下去 艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论今后遇上多么痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定会有人向你伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要相信那人 一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我很快就被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.15,0:22:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今都不知道阿尔的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 你受苦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗妹妹肯定就是艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这样一来就不是姆伽罗妹妹就成男的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 还想跟他一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定是米迦勒大人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦勒大人？谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我想见见那个叫姆伽罗的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越狱是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这监狱岛越狱的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今还没出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们要开创先河了 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 贞贞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.95,0:23:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是阿萨谢顶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是谢顶 是谢尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 谢尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 下回 神击的巴哈姆特Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么定了 谢尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫阿萨谢尔 这很重要